chav1961.purelib.fsys.interfaces.FileSystemInterface

Packages that use FileSystemInterface 
Package Description
chav1961.purelib.basic
This package contains a set of classes for the basic abilities of the library.
chav1961.purelib.fsys
This package contains a set of FileSystemInterface implementations and a factory to get access to them.
chav1961.purelib.fsys.interfaces
This package contains description of general File system interfaces.
chav1961.purelib.nanoservice
This package contains implementation of NanoService interface and a set of utility classes for it.
chav1961.purelib.nanoservice.interfaces
This package contains an API to use with NanoService implementations.
chav1961.purelib.ui.swing.useful
This package contains a set of useful classes to use in the Swing applications.

    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  AbstractFileSystem
    This abstract class implements the most of all FileSystemInterface functionality.

    This class implements the file system interface in the RAM.
    class  FileSystemOnClassLoader  
    class  FileSystemOnFile
    This class implements the file system interface on the usual file system.
    class  FileSystemOnFileSystem
    This class implements the file system interface on the standard file system mechanism in the Java 1.7 and later.
    class  FileSystemOnRMI
    This class implements the file system interface on remote server using standard Java RMI protocol.
    class  FileSystemOnXMLReadOnly
    This class implements the file system interface on the XML file content.
